<div class="answer-head">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$zhou-quan-43-90"
class="zm-item-link-avatar"
href="/people/zhou-quan-43-90">
<img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/625501830_s.jpg"
class="zm-list-avatar"
data-source="http://pic1.zhimg.com/625501830_s.jpg" />
</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$zhou-quan-43-90" href="/people/zhou-quan-43-90">周全</a>，<strong title="笔棍/游戏文案/懒蛋/屎尿屁专精" class="zu-question-my-bio">笔棍/游戏文案/懒蛋/屎尿屁专精</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="24">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$jun-lin-27-37" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/jun-lin-27-37" class="zg-link" title="君临">君临</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$huan-xia-91" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/huan-xia-91" class="zg-link" title="幻夏">幻夏</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$patrick-mei" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/patrick-mei" class="zg-link" title="Patrick MEI">Patrick MEI</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2176822" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">机器猫的初步故事设定，是展示很多神奇的道具。所以需要一个长期处于弱势的康夫来埃欺负，然后用道具来帮助他。<br>到了超长篇就不一样了。超长篇是大家一起应对危机，所以你看超长篇里的小朋友就显得很团结。<br>至于蜡笔小新……除了发怒的妈妈以外这故事里还有比他更强势的么？小朋友不团结，那就变成一个个被他纯虐的故事了。明显跟欢乐故事的初衷不符。


</div>

</div>
